<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h1 class="page-header page-header-icon page-header-icon-modules">@ViewBag.Title</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p>Available PowerShell moduels on the pull server. To upload a new module, use the <em>Upload</em> button and select a file that match the naming convention <strong>&lt;ModuleName&gt;_&lt;ModuleVersion&gt;.zip</strong>. The module needs to be formatted properly. Check the <a href="https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/dsc/pullserver#dsc-resource-module-package-format">help page</a> for more information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-12 table-buttons">
        <div class="btn btn-default table-fileupload">
            <span>Upload</span>
            <input id="modulesUploadButton" type="file" class="upload" />
        </div>
        <button id="modulesRefreshButton" class="btn btn-default table-refresh">Refresh</button>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-12" id="table-modules-loader">
        <p><i class="fa fa-refresh fa-spin fa-3x fa-fw"></i></p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-12 dsc-table" id="table-modules-content" style="display: none;">
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-hover">
                <colgroup>
                    <col style="width: 40%;" />
                    <col style="width: 15%;" />
                    <col style="width: 16%;" />
                    <col style="width: 13%;" />
                    <col style="width: 8%;" />
                    <col style="width: 8%;" />
                </colgroup>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Name</th>
                        <th>Version</th>
                        <th>Created</th>
                        <th>Checksum</th>
                        <th>Status</th>
                        <th></th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody></tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-12" id="table-modules-exception" style="display: none;">
        <p class="text-danger bg-danger">500 (Internal Server Error)</p>
    </div>
</div>
